, 200.0393, 202.7823, 203.7226, 204.4594, 202.9497, 204.0389, 203.2097, 203.0968, 202.8984, 200.742, 201.284, 201.5281, 201.523, 202.2931, 204.0412, 203.4757, 202.4476, 202.0769, 201.3048, 200.3399, 198.1672, 197.5611, 198.3377, 197.6618, 197.8859, 196.8732, 197.1425, 197.7768, 196.559, 196.2847, 196.7788, 196.1789, 196.7809, 197.7587, 198.4977, 198.1986, 197.8155, 198.3142, 198.447, 198.4401, 198.6151, 198.5351, 199.263, 199.632, 198.9003, 198.8638, 199.7733, 198.8265, 199.4898, 199.3599, 200.576, 199.4382, 198.8663, 198.9888, 197.3878, 198.8881, 197.6586, 197.0195, 197.7927, 195.8722, 196.6081, 194.8929, 196.3301, 196.6285, 197.7694, 197.4389, 200.0564, 202.5309, 199.6748, 198.8373, 199.2123, 198.4147, 198.4346, 198.1134, 197.7746, 197.0188, 197.8814, 198.0254, 198.6057, 199.5924, 199.8399, 199.2109, 198.7763, 198.7701, 198.3278, 199.4142, 198.7278, 198.5605, 198.9089, 198.8204, 196.923, 196.6491, 196.8951, 197.6575, 196.7602, 196.2673, 197.3507, 196.8343, 198.1399, 199.5229, 200.1014, 200.0105, 202.2427, 201.0591, 199.372, 198.6768, 199.6956, 200.0192, 200.6598, 201.6705, 201.4519, 202.16, 202.8362, 202.4699, 201.4159, 201.6373, 200.8159, 200.3517, 200.6422, 200.5821, 198.6613, 198.0623, 197.1682, 196.6616, 197.4823, 199.0806, 199.3946, 199.7533, 199.7037, 199.7516, 200.1424, 201.0414, 201.0168, 201.6125, 201.0854, 201.5691, 201.2392, 200.8181, 200.3209, 199.5054, 198.822, 199.5894, 199.1285, 200.5424, 199.7756, 199.6207, 200.5985, 202.2698, 203.0864, 201.3727, 199.6916, 199.6391, 198.4103, 198.8303, 198.4976, 197.9021, 198.5016, 199.4852, 198.7915, 197.9981, 197.7608, 196.3083, 196.9765, 196.557, 195.8301, 193.7252, 193.5892, 194.0705, 194.6731, 194.129, 194.566, 193.9799, 194.8162, 196.7237, 196.7643, 196.5555, 195.3816, 197.441, 197.6588, 197.9001, 199.1005, 197.5737, 195.7165, 194.826, 195.04, 196.1183, 196.813, 195.3785, 195.3833, 196.216, 197.2148, 198.4222, 199.1612, 199.0587, 199.5217, 200.3565, 203.2428, 206.7429, 206.9514, 206.9553, 209.1434, 211.0281, 210.2009, 210.6487, 210.5628, 210.0091, 210.5165, 210.6611, 214.507, 217.8288, 216.0703, 214.0566, 213.7849, 211.0528, 213.7286, 213.2551, 212.0823, 212.844, 211.0031, 214.7063, 215.7375, 218.1439, 213.7761, 217.3655, 216.1457, 216.8201, 215.934, 215.1868, 215.1387, 212.604, 211.939, 211.7233, 210.6685, 211.5556, 211.8248, 211.9663, 213.3484, 214.1188, 213.1408, 212.3901, 210.3375], "summary_html": "<h1>商品量化基本面多因子框架</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本策略基于兴业证券的\"量化基本面\"(Quantamental)框架，将影响商品期货价格的因子分为基本面因子和情绪因子两大类。原文以螺纹钢为研究对象，使用宏观产业链数据（产量、库存、房地产投资等）构建基本面因子库。本复现将其扩展到全品种截面，利用日频基本面字段（展期收益、库存变化率、仓单变化率、累积展期收益动量）替代宏观数据，通过截面排名将因子值转换为[-1,1]的连续信号，等权组合后经波动率目标缩放和定期再平衡生成最终仓位。</p>\n<p>核心逻辑：低库存/高展期收益/低仓单的品种做多，反之做空。多因子组合分散了单一因子的风险，提升了信号稳健性。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.1</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>4.5%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.1%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-9.3%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.05</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.15</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.85</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.56 / 0.74</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.01</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.43</span></td><td>1.96</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.25</span></td><td>0.56</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.35</span></td><td>1.44</td><td>1.64</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.64</span></td><td>1.79</td><td>1.26</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.15</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.5</span></td><td>0.13</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">4.52</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>ry</code></td><td>展期收益</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>rycumprod</code></td><td>展期收益累乘</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>inventory_21</code></td><td>库存(21日)</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>receipt</code></td><td>仓单</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 10 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 10 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.2%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>39.3</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>库存变化率因子（Ave_CR）</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Ave\\_CR}(t) = \\frac{Inv(t)}{\\frac{1}{M}\\sum_{i=0}^{M-1}Inv(t-i)} - 1, \\quad M=90</div>\n<p>信号方向取反（库存下降 = 看多）。<span class=\"math-tex\">Inv</span> 优先取 <code>inventory_21</code>，缺失时回退到 <code>receipt</code>。</p>\n<p><strong>展期收益因子（RY）</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{ry\\_factor} = ry_t</div>\n<p>正值 = backwardation = 近月溢价 = 看多。</p>\n<p><strong>仓单变化率因子</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Receipt\\_CR}(t) = \\frac{R(t)}{\\frac{1}{60}\\sum_{i=0}^{59}R(t-i)} - 1</div>\n<p>信号方向取反（仓单减少 = 看多）。</p>\n<p><strong>累积展期收益动量因子</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{ryc\\_mom}(t) = \\frac{\\text{rycumprod}(t)}{\\text{rycumprod}(t-60)} - 1</div>\n<p>正值 = carry趋势增强 = 看多。</p>\n<p><strong>截面信号</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_j(t) = \\left(\\text{rank}_{cs}(F_j(t)) - 0.5\\right) \\times 2 \\in [-1, 1]</div>\n<p><strong>多因子组合</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{combo}(t) = \\frac{1}{K}\\sum_{j=1}^{K}\\text{signal}_j(t)</div>\n<p><strong>波动率目标缩放</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position} = \\text{combo} \\times \\frac{\\sigma_{\\text{target}}}{\\hat{\\sigma}_{60d} \\times \\sqrt{252}}</div>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>Sharpe 0.60 (fund6_raw), 6个基本面因子+3个情绪因子全实现; combo变体反而劣于fund-only; TS IC为负(-0.003)</td><td>基线: 6个基本面因子(inv_cr/ry/basis/seat/profit/receipt_cr) + 3个动量(20/60/120), 等权组合, hold=20</td><td>fund6 Sharpe 0.60, combo仅0.27-0.41, 情绪因子拖累</td></tr><tr><td>R2 (关键突破)</td><td>需要提升Sharpe至0.8; profit和memberdiff20可能是噪声; h10可能优于h20</td><td><strong>核心4因子</strong>(inv_cr+ry+basis+receipt_cr), 去掉profit和memberdiff20; 添加IC gate变体; h10/h20网格</td><td><strong>core4_h10 Sharpe 0.93</strong> 首次通过; IC gate反而有害(0.20); h10 &gt; h20</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>进一步优化; 与gtja_basis高相关(0.71); 尝试差异化</td><td>添加<strong>rycumprod动量因子</strong>; 创建<strong>nobasic变体</strong>(去掉basis, 用ryc_mom替代); 测试inv lookback=[60,90,120]</td><td><strong>nobasic_h10 Sharpe 1.06</strong>; core4_M120也达1.00; 半样本H1/H2=1.41/0.99</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折</strong>: R2去掉profit和memberdiff20(噪声因子), 从0.60跃升至0.93; R3引入rycumprod动量并创建无basis变体, 进一步提升至1.06, 同时降低了与已有因子库(gtja_basis)的相关性。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全商品期货(58个品种参与)</li>\n<li><strong>数据字段</strong>: <code>ry</code>(展期收益), <code>rycumprod</code>(累积展期收益), <code>inventory_21</code>(库存), <code>receipt</code>(仓单), <code>close</code>(收盘价)</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 10天再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>多空比例</strong>: 多48.7% / 空46.9% / 空仓4.4%</li>\n<li><strong>盈利品种</strong>: V(PVC), I(铁矿石), J(焦炭), RB(螺纹钢), JM(焦煤) -- 黑色系和化工品因子效果最强</li>\n<li><strong>亏损品种</strong>: SM(硅锰), C(玉米), RM(菜粕), AU(黄金), AG(白银) -- 贵金属和农产品因子效果差</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 与因子库中jpmorgan_bmom的相关性0.65(边界水平)\n<p>- 基本面数据存在NaN(覆盖率70-97%), 需mean_horizontal自动跳过 - 2023-2024年Sharpe接近零, 近两年信号偏弱 - 原文针对单品种(螺纹钢), 扩展到全品种后信号被部分品种稀释</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>INV_LOOKBACK</code></td><td><code>90</code></td><td>库存变化率滚动窗口</td></tr><tr><td><code>RECEIPT_LOOKBACK</code></td><td><code>60</code></td><td>仓单变化率滚动窗口</td></tr><tr><td><code>RYC_MOM_PERIOD</code></td><td><code>60</code></td><td>累积展期收益动量周期</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_DAYS</code></td><td><code>10</code></td><td>再平衡间隔</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9954</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.57s</li>\n</ul>"}